data.description:
This stunning condo is the PERFECT mix of modern updates & historic details. Step inside to HUMUNGOUS windows with panoramic views of Broughton street, those, along with the SOARING ceilings & the OPEN floorplan- make this unit light, bright and airy. Did I mention the original hardwood floors and exposed brick that radiate Savannah charm?!

The kitchen has been fully updated, with stainless steel appliances & granite countertops- great for ENTERTAINING with seating for 6. The show-stopping curved hallway will take you to a designer-renovated bath complete with gorgeous walk-in shower. The primary bedroom provides a fantastic space to unwind & 2 large closets for abundant storage. 

Bonus: 1 of the few buildings in the area to be warrantable for easy financing.

Talk about LOCATION! This downtown loft is in a secure building the HEART of it all! While the BEST shopping is on Broughton, you’re also STEPS from the HOTTEST restaurants, bars, & entertainment Savannah has to offer!
